thread.title: Sonia & Paul
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Sonia & Paul

author: Sonia & Paul
title: Sonia & Paul
text:
We are very happy with the service and support we received in the process of selling our home. Carl and his team where very professional and where always happy to answer any questions we may have had.
It was a smooth process for us with a amazing result.
Will definitely be doing business with the team, if i ever need to again. Thank you all for all your hard work. And Duncan the auctioneer well let's just say he knows his job.. fantastic
